{"title":"在Linux系统上开启BBR加速","uid":"e121e1d4dc52e3ebdd9b65d941d97aa7","slug":"在Linux系统上开启BBR加速","date":"2022-07-17T06:46:34.000Z","updated":"2022-07-18T04:13:13.251Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/在Linux系统上开启BBR加速.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h1><p>Google BBR是一款Google开发的拥堵控制算法，通过优化和控制TCP的拥塞，充分利用带宽并降低延迟，使得服务器的带宽得到合理化应用。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h1 id=\"文章介绍\"><a href=\"#文章介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文章介绍\"></a>文章介绍</h1><p>本篇文章我们将在CentOS7以及Debian11上演示开启Google BBR。</p>\n<h1 id=\"在CentOS7上开启Google-BBR\"><a href=\"#在CentOS7上开启Google-BBR\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在CentOS7上开启Google BBR\"></a>在CentOS7上开启Google BBR</h1><h2 id=\"一、升级系统内核\"><a href=\"#一、升级系统内核\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、升级系统内核\"></a>一、升级系统内核</h2><p>首先查看内核版本，确定自己是否需要更新内核(可略过)，版本如果大于4.9就可以不用升级，但建议升级。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">cat</span> /etc/redhat-release \n$ <span class=\"token function\">uname</span> -a<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>使用这个命令您可以查看系统安装的所有内核</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">rpm</span> -qa <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> kernel<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>启用elrepo仓库</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">rpm</span> --import https://www.elrepo.org/RPM-GPG-KEY-elrepo.org <span class=\"token comment\">#导入公共密钥</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">rpm</span> -Uvh http://www.elrepo.org/elrepo-release-7.0-2.el7.elrepo.noarch.rpm <span class=\"token comment\">#安装elrepo仓库的yum源</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>安装最新版本的内核</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ yum --enablerepo<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>elrepo-kernel <span class=\"token function\">install</span> kernel-ml -y<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>查看系统已安装的所有内核，并显示序号</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">awk</span> -F<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>' <span class=\"token string\">'$1==\"menuentry \" &#123;print i++ \" : \" $2&#125;'</span> /etc/grub2.cfg<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>设置新版本内核为默认启动并重启，后面的数字就是上一步操作显示的序号</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ grub2-set-default <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.